function Start()
	--Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idLockpick, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idLockpick, false)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idWatcher, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idWatcher, false)
	
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONV_ATTACK, idWatcher)
	
	--Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idLockpick) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idLockpick) then
		Hydra.ActorTriggerPhaseJump(idLockpick)
	end
end
